Divided by religion,  united by humanity

Pakistan 🇵🇰 💖 India 🇮🇳 

The Wire Pakistan team has initiated a compassionate project to provide an artificial limb to a camel in distress. This effort is designed to alleviate the suffering of the injured animal, showcasing a heartwarming commitment to animal welfare. 

The artificial limb, generously provided by Rajendera from India, represents a significant step towards improving the quality of life for the camel. The prosthetic limb is scheduled to be sent to Dubai on Monday.
